data.description: Looking for your first home or are you an investor looking for a nice rental. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home is just what you need. Move in ready! Convenient location. Very close to all in town amenities! Call today for your personal showing!
data.whatILove: Open floor plan, cheap electric, less than one mile from schools and stores. Master bath. Nice neighbors. Small metal shed and a garage New kitchen floor. Glass top electric range. Gutters installed in 2015. Central heat and air.
